702347f-a.title: Brooklyn: 4th Avenue - 75th Street
702347f-a.text:
Fourth Ave., west side, between 75th (left) and 74th (right) Streets,
showing the Church of the Good Shepherd (Lutheran). Also shown are
Nos. 371 to 365 (fore to background) 75th Street, north side, west of
Fourth Ave.
December 17, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
